00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:02.680
Marco, that's the third game out the way as well.

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:05.480
And the 0-0 scoreline has no bearing on things because we were already through.

00:00:06.200 --> 00:00:15.520
Yes, we're still a bit disappointed though because the lads squandered a hatful of chances.

00:00:15.800 --> 00:00:25.360
That is a little disappointing but at least they went into it in the right frame of mind,

00:00:25.400 --> 00:00:30.720
they always tried to play good football against a team that really didn't do anything at all.

00:00:30.760 --> 00:00:34.040
Sometimes if you don't get that little bit of luck,

00:00:34.040 --> 00:00:36.040
or if you're not quite clinical enough,

00:00:36.080 --> 00:00:38.680
you can end up with a result like this.

00:00:38.720 --> 00:00:40.560
A quick assessment of these first three games?

00:00:41.560 --> 00:00:46.520
Good. We know we're going into the knockout stage now where it really starts to matter,

00:00:46.520 --> 00:00:59.040
so we have to get our energy back and come through the games that will enable us to reach the final.

00:00:59.240 --> 00:01:01.720
So Daniele, you've reached your first goal.

00:01:01.800 --> 00:01:04.880
Qualification was already in the bag but you finished the group with seven points.

00:01:04.960 --> 00:01:10.680
Yeah, obviously it was important for us to go through as seeds.

00:01:10.920 --> 00:01:14.680
And we managed that, even though we didn't get the three points today.

00:01:14.760 --> 00:01:22.800
The 0-0 doesn't really do us justice but we achieved our target and that's the main thing.

00:01:23.240 --> 00:01:25.240
What shape are Juventus in going into the last 16?

