We're fired up, definitely, and very ambitious because we want to go all the way â€“ and we're confident we can pull it off.

00:01:36.760 --> 00:01:41.040
We've got a good group of players here and we're totally up for it,

00:01:41.040 --> 00:01:46.120
determined to get through the next round and go as far as possible.

00:01:46.240 --> 00:01:48.800
So let's say we want the same Juventus team that we've seen over the last four months,

00:01:48.840 --> 00:01:50.680
when you haven't put a foot wrong.

00:01:50.720 --> 00:01:59.360
Yes, we have to keep on this path but without looking back too much,

00:01:59.400 --> 00:02:05.480
because what we've done up until now doesn't really count for an awful lot.

00:02:05.560 --> 00:02:12.440
What lies ahead is what matters, the games we have coming up, the last 16 and the ones after that if we get there.

00:02:12.800 --> 00:02:16.000
Last question, how are you finding it in your first year with Juventus Primavera?

00:02:16.280 --> 00:02:23.520
I'm really happy here. I've supported Juventus since I was a boy so... it's amazing.

00:02:23.560 --> 00:02:34.720
