00:02:34.760 --> 00:02:36.960
because I always used to play in a four-man defence.

00:02:36.960 --> 00:02:44.680
But I quickly settled into the three-man system this year, whether I'm playing right, left or centre.

00:02:44.760 --> 00:02:45.920
So yeah, everything's going great!

